          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Two stacks containing each 9 target foils interleaved",
                " with natural Ti foils were activated.",
                "Irradiation was made at 21 MeV deuteron beam at the VUB",
                " cyclotron, approximately 150 nA for about 1 hour.",
                "The samples were first measured about 2 h after EOB and",
                " assessment of the activity continued over a 1 month",
                " decay period, at different sample-detector distances",
                " (5-45 cm).",
                "The SRIM 2006 code was used for estimation of the",
                " energy degradation in each foil of the stacks.",
                "Decay and spectrometric characteristics of the",
                " investigated radionuclides were taken from Nudat2."
              ]
            }
          ],
